=== Iṛumen ===
Amdan-nsen uɣrid 7,590,000, azgen deg-sen ttidiren deg [[Uruppa tasemrant]]. 90.4% d ikritiyen, 4.4% d inselmen ma d 5.1% war [[ajjed|asɣan]]<ref>[http://www.joshuaproject.net/people-clusters.php?peo2=354&tab=3 People Group Cluster - Romany :: Joshua Project<!-- Azwel -->] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130826013729/http://joshuaproject.net/people-clusters.php?peo2=354&tab=3 |date=26 ɣuct 2013}}</ref>. Bṭan ɣer waṭas n tegrawin, gar-asent: 
* '''Iflaksen''': Amdan-nsen 2,015,000. Ttenfufuden s tuget deg yakk ideggan n umadal aladɣa deg [[Ṛumanya]] d [[Brazil]] d [[Iwunak Yedduklen n Temrikt]], Tutlayt-nsen tagejdant d [[tutlayt tarument|tarument]] s [[tantala|tentala-ines]] taflakst
* '''Irumen ibelkanen''': amdan-nsen 1,368,000, ttilin deg Uruppa s tuget aladɣa deg [[Unranya]] d [[Sirbya]] d [[Bulgarya]],  [[tutlayt tarument|tarument]] s [[tantala|tentala-ines]] tabelkant ma deg Sirbya lan (sɛan) tantala tusligt. Tuget-nsen d ikritiyen anagar deg [[Turkya]] d [[Masidunya tagafant]] d [[Iran]] d [[Lezzayer]] d [[Ṛumanya]] anda rṭṭafaren asɣan ineslem 

[[Tugna:P15079.jpg|thumb|right|Iziganen n Kalu di [[Spanya]]]]
* '''Iziganen n ukalu''': Amdan-nsen 995,000, ttidiren di [[Spanya]] d [[Tigzirin Tiknariyin]] d [[Brazil]], ttmeslayen tutlayin n yideggan anda ttidiren yakk d tutlayt n Kalu s talɣa tasnawt

